# Debug & Logging Standards - MoonProject

## 1. Tag Convention

Mỗi Debug.Log PHẢI có tag format: `[ClassName]` hoặc `[Module.ClassName]`

```csharp
Debug.Log("[Farm] Planted wheat at pos=(2,3)");
Debug.LogWarning("[Animal] Feed failed: not enough energy");
Debug.LogError("[DataController] Save failed: file corrupted");
```

## 2. Log Levels

| Level | Dùng khi | Ví dụ |
|-------|----------|-------|
| `Debug.Log` | Thông tin debug, flow tracking | `[Farm] Growth complete` |
| `Debug.LogWarning` | Bất thường nhưng recoverable | `[Config] Remote config timeout, using cache` |
| `Debug.LogError` | Lỗi nghiêm trọng, cần fix | `[Save] Failed to write data.dat` |
| `Debug.LogException` | Exception cần stack trace | Trong catch blocks |

## 3. Conditional Compilation

Code mới PHẢI wrap debug logs trong `#if DEV_LOGS`:

```csharp
public class Farm : MonoBehaviour
{
    public void TryHarvest()
    {
#if DEV_LOGS
        Debug.Log($"[Farm] TryHarvest at {CellPos}, plantId={state.plantId}");
#endif
        // harvest logic...
    }
}
```

### Ngoại lệ - KHÔNG cần wrap:
- `Debug.LogError` / `Debug.LogException` → luôn log (cần biết lỗi trong production)
- Analytics events → luôn gửi

## 4. Structured Log Format

Cho thông tin phức tạp, dùng key=value format:

```csharp
#if DEV_LOGS
Debug.Log($"[IAP] Purchase complete: pack={packName}, price={price}, currency={currency}");
Debug.Log($"[Leaderboard] Score updated: userId={userId}, score={newScore}, rank={rank}");
#endif
```

## 5. Performance Logging (khuyến nghị)

```csharp
#if DEV_LOGS
public static class PerfLog
{
    private static readonly Dictionary<string, System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch> _timers = new();

    public static void Begin(string label)
    {
        var sw = System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.StartNew();
        _timers[label] = sw;
    }

    public static void End(string label)
    {
        if (_timers.TryGetValue(label, out var sw))
        {
            sw.Stop();
            Debug.Log($"[Perf] {label}: {sw.ElapsedMilliseconds}ms");
            _timers.Remove(label);
        }
    }
}

// Usage:
PerfLog.Begin("LoadMap");
// ... load map logic
PerfLog.End("LoadMap"); // Output: [Perf] LoadMap: 342ms
#endif
```

## 6. Migration từ code hiện tại

Code cũ dùng `Debug.Log` trực tiếp → khi touch file:
1. Thêm tag `[ClassName]`
2. Wrap trong `#if DEV_LOGS` (trừ LogError/LogException)
3. KHÔNG migration hàng loạt - chỉ khi sửa file

---

### Ví dụ ĐÚNG

```csharp
public void OnCompletePurchase(Product product)
{
    Debug.LogError($"[IAP] Purchase failed: productId={product.definition.id}"); // Error luôn log

#if DEV_LOGS
    Debug.Log($"[IAP] Purchase success: id={product.definition.id}, receipt={product.receipt?.Substring(0, 50)}...");
#endif

    ProcessReward(product);
}
```

### Ví dụ SAI

```csharp
public void OnCompletePurchase(Product product)
{
    Debug.Log("purchase complete"); // Không tag, không structured, không conditional
    Debug.Log(product.receipt); // Log toàn bộ receipt (PII risk, spam)
    ProcessReward(product);
}
```
